    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "identity",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 380,
      "width": 900,
      "height": 430,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#e7f5ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "frameId": null
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "identity-text",
      "x": 90,
      "y": 405,
      "width": 840,
      "height": 360,
      "text": "Bounded Context: Identity\n\nDefine a porta consumidora PermissionChecker:\nhasPermission(actorRole, permissionKey) → boolean\n\nEnforcement nos casos de uso:\n• GetAuthenticatedUserContext\n• UpdateOwnProfile\n• ChangePassword\n• ToggleAccountStatus\n• AdminResetPassword\n\nInvariantes contextuais continuam em Identity:\nADMIN não gerencia nem redefine senha de OWNER.",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "strokeColor": "#1864ab",
      "frameId": null
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "access-control",
      "x": 1030,
      "y": 360,
      "width": 740,
      "height": 470,
      "strokeColor": "#e67700",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff4e6",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "roughness": 0,
      "frameId": null
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "access-control-text",
      "x": 1060,
      "y": 385,
      "width": 680,
      "height": 400,
      "text": "Bounded Context: Access Control\n\nmodules/access-control\n\nPERMISSION_CATALOG\n• fonte primária única\n• 9 PermissionKeys fechadas\n• metadados de apresentação\n\nRolePermissionMap\n• OWNER: 9 • ADMIN: 9 • USER: 3\n\nhasPermission: política pura e total\nparsePermissionKey: somente na fronteira\n\nSem Prisma e SEM dependência de Identity.",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "strokeColor": "#d9480f",
      "frameId": null
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "participants",
      "x": 1840,
      "y": 380,
      "width": 900,
      "height": 430,
      "strokeColor": "#2b8a3e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ebfbee",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "frameId": null
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "participants-text",
      "x": 1870,
      "y": 405,
      "width": 840,
      "height": 360,
      "text": "Bounded Context: Participants\n\nChange: implement-participant-registration-mvp\n\nConsome o contrato público de Access Control:\n• CreateBettingAgent\n• ListBettingAgents\n• GetBettingAgent\n\nPermissionKeys:\n• participants.betting-agents.create\n• participants.betting-agents.list\n• participants.betting-agents.read\n\nOrdem explícita: implementar após Access Control.",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "strokeColor": "#2b8a3e",
      "frameId": null
    },
