      "text": "apps/backend — Composition Root e fronteira HTTP",
      "fontSize": 22,
      "strokeColor": "#0b7285",
      "frameId": null
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "adapter",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 1010,
      "width": 650,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "AccessControlPermissionChecker\n\nImplementa PermissionChecker de Identity.\nDelega para hasPermission de Access Control.\n\nA implementação concreta permanece fora dos bounded contexts.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "strokeColor": "#0b7285",
      "frameId": null
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "matrix-endpoint",
      "x": 1080,
      "y": 1010,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "GET /api/access-control/role-permissions\n\nJwtCookieAuthGuard + hasPermission\n(access-control.role-permissions.read)\n\nOWNER/ADMIN → matriz completa\nUSER → FORBIDDEN",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "strokeColor": "#0b7285",
      "frameId": null
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "me-endpoint",
      "x": 1720,
      "y": 1010,
      "width": 660,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "GET /api/access-control/me/permissions\n\nSomente JwtCookieAuthGuard.\nSEM hasPermission prévio.\n\nQualquer autenticado → somente as próprias\npermissões efetivas.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "strokeColor": "#0b7285",
      "frameId": null
    },
